		<title>Malaysia is rushing into AI faster than anyone. Its governance gap is the price</title>
		<link>https://techwireasia.com/2026/04/ai-governance-gap-malaysia/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Dashveenjit Kaur]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 07:00:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[AI & Intelligence]]></category>
